==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flection
<hw>Flec"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Flexion</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of bending, or state
of being bent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The variation of words by declension, comparison, or
conjugation; inflection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flectional</ent>⟦br⟧
